final encounters at the world championships:
</P>
<P>
Sweden bt China 5-1 in 1983
</P>
<P>
China bt Sweden 5-0 in 1985
</P>
<P>
China bt Sweden 5-0 in 1987
</P>
<P>
Sweden bt China 5-0 in 1989
</P>
<P>
Sweden bt China 3-1 in 1993
</P>
<P>
China bt Sweden 3-2 in 1995
