<DOCNO> XIE19970428.0066 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-04-28 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Forum Commemorates Late Leader Ye Jianying </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 28 (Xinhua) -- The Central Committee of the
Communist Party of China today held a forum at the Great Hall of
the People to mark the 100th anniversary of the birth of Ye
Jianying, a State leader who passed away in 1986.
</P>
<P>
President Jiang Zemin made an important and lengthy speech at the
meeting, which was attended by more than 300 people, including
senior Party and State leaders of Li Peng, Qiao Shi, Li Ruihuan,
Zhu Rongji, Liu Huaqing, Hu Jintao and Rong Yiren.
</P>
<P>
"We commemorate Comrade Ye Jianying and all other proletarian
revolutionaries to enable the people of this generation and later
generations to better carry forward their unfulfilled
revolutionary behests and their unaccomplished causes and to
learn from their great thoughts and noble work style, in order to
make our country more prosperous and powerful," Jiang said.
</P>
<P>
Liu Huaqing, a member of the Standing Committee of the
Political Bureau of the CPC Central Committee and vice-chairman of
the Central Military Commission, noted that Ye was a founder of
the Chinese People's Liberation Army and a renowned military
strategist of the Party and the army.
</P>
<P>
Ye demonstrated an outstanding ability for military strategies
and a grasp of the art of warfare, Liu said.
</P>
<P>
Wang Hanbin, an alternate member of the Political Bureau of the
CPC Central Committee and vice-chairman of the Standing Committee
of the National People's Congress, elaborated on Ye's contributions
to China's effort to build socialist democracy and institute a
socialist legal system.
</P>
<P>
He also said that Ye showed great concern about the great
cause of reunification of the motherland.
</P>
<P>
Henry Fok Ying-tung, vice-chairman of the National Committee of
the Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference (CPPCC),
said that Ye was greatly concerned with the affairs related Chinese
nationals living abroad, calling him a model in uniting overseas
Chinese.
</P>
<P>
Hu Jintao, a member of the Standing Committee of the Political
Bureau of the CPC Central Committee and member of the Secretariat
of the CPC Central Committee, said that "we must carry forward the
unfulfilled wishes of the older generation of proletarians and
carry victoriously into the 21st century the cause of socialism
they initiated, so as to build our country into a prosperous,
democratic and civilized one.
</P>
<P>
"This is our best commemoration for Comrade Ye Jianying," said
Hu, who presided over the meeting.
</P>
<P>
In another development, a photo album and the collected works
of Ye Jianying have been published by the Central Literature
Publishing House and were distributed nationwide as of today.
</P>
<P>
The album contains more than 500 photos depicting Ye at various
historical periods, and the collected works include Ye's important
military writings between 1933 and 1982.  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
