shares changing hands, CRA lost 10 cents, and WMC dropped 13.6
cents.
</P>
<P>
Australia's most profitable bank, National Australia Bank, was
the top traded stock, with 27.04 million shares changing hands.
</P>
<P>
National turnover totaled 347.51 million shares traded, with
value topping 1.41 billion Australian dollars (1.09 billion US
dollars).  
</P>
