<TEXT>
<P>
NEW YORK, April 27 (Xinhua) -- Michael Jordan scored 55 points
dominated the fourth quarter with 20 of of Chicago's 23 Sunday
when the Bulls edged the Washington Bullets 109-104 for a 2-0
