<HEADLINE> Hollywood to Buy Chinese Film With Patriotic Theme </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, April 28 (Xinhua) -- Hollywood is interested in
buying a film about Chinese campaigns early in this century
against British troops invading Tibet.
</P>
<P>
Sources from the film industry told Xinhua here today that
several Hollywood companies like Warner Bros. and 20th Century Fox
have contacted the producer, the Shanghai Film and Television
Corporation, about acquiring the film, which has caused a
patriotic sensation in China.
</P>
