the Qinghai-Tibet Plateau against British troops early in this
century.
</P>
<P>
The American actors Paul Newman and Nicholas Love starred in
the film, which was released across China last weekend.
</P>
<P>
The film cost more than 15 million yuan (nearly eight million
US dollars), one of the biggest expenditures in Chinese film
history.
</P>
<P>
Several film companies from Britain, France and Australia are
also negotiating for the rights to show the movie.  
